{"tid":1954913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港 本土派最早提出「初選」慨念","createTime":"2020-04-02T07:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T10:51:50.000Z","uid":134071,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4278536b37a9f779eb2743a1876f97b57e1283fb","tid":1954913,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:02:59.000Z","msg":"本土派係最早提出「初選」慨念, 並非泛民.<br />\n<br />\n如果初選攪得成, 唔係泛民騎劫本土派, 而係本土派成功改變泛民.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%A8%E9%9D%9E%E5%90%8C%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%BA-%E9%9D%92%E6%94%BF%E6%A2%81%E9%A0%8C%E6%81%86-%E5%9B%A0%E7%A5%A8%E6%BA%90%E9%87%8D%E7%96%8A%E9%A0%88%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8-%E4%B8%8D%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%90%8C%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%BA/?fbclid=IwAR1m3xBY4JUQeuf5ddGRqtqxU0YebBR5yw0T2NLTijDPo6hWpDE0oo5cE6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E9%259D%2592%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25A2%2581%25E9%25A0%258C%25E6%2581%2586-%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%25BA%2590%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2596%258A%25E9%25A0%2588%25E5%2588%259D%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1m3xBY4JUQeuf5ddGRqtqxU0YebBR5yw0T2NLTijDPo6hWpDE0oo5cE6g&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUhZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=ed403f14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E9%259D%2592%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25A2%2581%25E9%25A0%258C%25E6%2581%2586-%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%25BA%2590%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2596%258A%25E9%25A0%2588%25E5%2588%259D%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1m3xBY4JUQeuf5ddGRqtqxU0YebBR5yw0T2NLTijDPo6hWpDE0oo5cE6g&h=3922cd53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%A8%E9%9D%9E%E5%90%8C%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%BA-%E9%9D%92%E6%94%BF%E6%A2%81%E9%A0%8C%E6%81%86-%E5%9B%A0%E7%A5%A8%E6%BA%90%E9%87%8D%E7%96%8A%E9%A0%88%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8-%E4%B8%8D%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%90%8C%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%BA/?fbclid=IwAR1m3xBY4JUQeuf5ddGRqtqxU0YebBR5yw0T2NLTijDPo6hWpDE0oo5cE6g</a></span><br />\n<br />\n公民黨非同路人？ 青政梁頌恆：因票源重疊須初選 不考慮是否同路人<br />\n2015/12/7 &mdash; 12:55<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》今日報道，青年新政梁頌恆受訪時表示公民黨並非同路人，報道刊出後引起熱議，梁則在facebook個人專頁批評《蘋果》報道「膠作」。目前外界普遍質疑「非同路人為何初選？」梁頌恆接受本網查詢時稱，應否舉行初選，要考慮的是雙方票源有否重疊，而非考慮是否「同路人」。他形容，希望在「非保皇陣營」透過初選，可減低資源虛耗及爭拗，令「非保皇陣營」在新東補選毋須相撞。<br />\n<br />\n被問到青年新政對「同路人」定義為何，梁頌恆稱，如以「同路人」來分界，「可能好多人都係同路人」。梁頌恆指，青年新政在法治、民主的追求上，與公民黨相近，不能否認票源因而會有重疊；而當講到本土意識時，青年新政與一些本土派又有共同基礎，支持者差不多，今次新東補選任期短但消耗資源不少，認為初選是最有成本效益的方法。梁頌恆指初選「唔係分同唔同路人」 ，強調看的是票源重疊問題，舉例稱自己絕不會考慮與黃成智初選。<br />\n<br />\n他認為坊間有先入為主的想法，本土派認為青政是「泛民B隊」，泛民認為青政是「黃毓民B隊」，因有這樣的懷疑，才會要求青政表態誰是同路人。<br />\n<br />\n梁頌恆又指，自己在上週五接受《壹錘定音》訪問後，未有接受《蘋果》的訪問，稱青年新政稍後會發聲明，批評《蘋果》今日的報道，是根據上週五的《壹錘定音》「二次創作個報道出嚟」。"},{"pid":"284fcdc93c416ac6c0fe5eac7d30a1fe7a72207d","tid":1954913,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:03:28.000Z","msg":"正視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b944c425b2ade4be6bf57fd67e5ceee4c0c486c","tid":1954913,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2041d33d7d9e4bb72abc242ae4efa727728a1dc","tid":1954913,"uid":292710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"284fcdc93c416ac6c0fe5eac7d30a1fe7a72207d","tid":1954913,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:03:28.000Z","msg":"正視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cla